HEADWORD: Pancarte
<hw>Pan"carte`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. LL.
<ets>pancharta</ets>. See <er>Pan-</er>, and <er>Carte</er>.]</ety>
